==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oaf
<hw>Oaf</hw> <pr>(⟦omac⟧f)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Auf</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Originally, an elf's child; a
changeling left by fairies or goblins; hence, a deformed or foolish
child; a simpleton; an idiot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A clumsy or awkward person.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> klutz, clod, lummox, stumblebum.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oafish</ent>⟦br⟧
